node.text: I can’t believe it was 4 years ago today that I launched Uncommon James out of a room in my house. It’s incredible what we’ve done in those 4 short years- I sometimes still can’t believe it’s real. Thankful for everyone’s support...it’s because of you guys that I’m able to live a dream...and I will never forget that. Here’s a look back at the very first video we ever shot at our first campaign shoot. Feels like yesterday ♥️
